                    In alignment with our values, MAL-X Software is committed to building technology that creates lasting positive impact — for our clients, their users, and the communities they serve.
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    @{
                        var values = new[] {
                            ("Security First", "We build with security and privacy by design in every layer of our systems."),
